subject: Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: Joe Dombrowski of Cannondale-Garmin made a dominant move near the finish of Stage 6 in the Tour of Utah, riding solo to victory at Snowbird Ski Resort and assuming the overall lead.
